name: 2018 DIGITAL FORCE - DIGITAL IMPACT
content: Genesis Future Summits presents DIGITAL FORCE - DIGITAL IMPACT - an educational & exciting Summit, focused on the current & future impact of technological innovation, digital marketing ‘need-to-know’ trends as well as inspiring entrepreneurial leadership sessions to help advance your personal brand, career & business. Well-known Speakers - Industry Experts - will provide stimulating & inspiring discussions; an interactive Exhibition Hall showcasing innovative companies’ products & services. Embrace the Future - Join Us in Calgary, AB - November 26-29, 2018
